            <title>[CASSANDRA-5865] NPE when you mistakenly set listen_address to 0.0.0.0</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-5865</link>
                <project id="12310865" key="CASSANDRA">Apache Cassandra</project>
